text: CHEESECURDS WERE SO GOOD OMG.literally amazing go here for sure. The best cheese curds of all time

Outstanding cheese curds and mouth watering gourmet burgers, Leia's Lunchbox was incredible at the farmers' market.  Cheese Curds have a moment of glory where they are hot, crispy, melted, and wonderful.  At Leia's Lunchbox, you watch them pull them fresh from the fryer and hand them to you.  And don't miss out on the cookie dough!  Holy cow fried cookie dough was amazing!

fell in love with the bacon and bleu burger with the raspberry sauce. very great after a late night of studying on the way home from memorial library, or during a night out with friends when they are on state street!
